                    nesciunt voluptas, a corporis. Mollitia, aspernatur vel laboriosam adipisci necessitatibus
                    reiciendis vero id eos laudantium facere deleniti neque quis? Placeat vel nulla cupiditate alias
                    adipisci beatae suscipit odit! Dolores ad ipsam recusandae, animi eveniet praesentium laborum.
                </p>
                <div class="pt-10">
                    <a
                        href=""
                        class="bg-sky-500/50 border border-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-500/70 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg shadow-sky-500 text-white rounded-md py-1 px-4 text-xs transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out lg:text-sm lg:py-2"
                        >Download Resume</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-5 lg:px-20 mt-16">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
            <!-- Education -->
            <div>
                <div class="text-start max-w-xl mb-4">
